   Chen, Ying-Hao; Ruan, Shanq-Jang, Natl Taiwan Univ Sci \& Technol, Dept Elect \& Comp Engn, Taipei, Taiwan.
   Chen, Pei-fu, Far Eastern Mem Hosp, Dept Anesthesiol, 21,Sec 2,Nanya S Rd, New Taipei City 220, Taiwan.
