   Hossen, Md. Fahim; Noor, Md. Tajim An, Rajshahi Univ Engn \& Technol, Dept Elect \& Comp Engn, Rajshahi 6204, Bangladesh.
   Arselene Ayari, Mohamed, Qatar Univ, Dept Civil Engn, Doha, Qatar.},
